id: pm-0rjf
title: Release @unbrained/pm-cli after 2026.5.4
description: "Prepare, verify, and publish the next pm CLI release after 2026.5.4 with compatibility migration gates, GitHub issue remediation, telemetry/Sentry review, changelog/docs updates, local CI/CD parity, and public npm/npx/bunx/GitHub verification."
type: Chore
status: in_progress
priority: 0
tags[8]: automation,ci,compatibility,github,pm-cli,release,sentry,telemetry
created_at: "2026-05-05T18:05:05.397Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-05T21:10:19.818Z"
deadline: "2026-05-06T18:05:05.397Z"
assignee: codex-release-agent
author: codex-release-agent
estimated_minutes: 360
acceptance_criteria: No previous-version tracker data breaks; GitHub issues #20 and #21 are documented and resolved or explicitly triaged; scheduled auto-release and release workflows only publish after strict green gates and actual changes; changelog and release notes are generated from pm evidence; npm/npx/bunx/GitHub publish verification succeeds.
parent: pm-rnpb
dependencies[1]{id,kind,created_at,author,source_kind}:
  pm-rnpb,parent,"2026-05-05T18:05:05.397Z",codex-release-agent,null
comments[15]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-05T18:05:05.397Z",codex-release-agent,"Duplicate-check evidence: ran pm context --limit 10,pm search release 2026.5.5 auto release compatibility GitHub issue 20 frontmatter issue 21 npm install --limit 20,pm list-open --limit 30,pm list-in-progress --limit 30,and inspected prior closed release item pm-0qv7. No open release item covers this post-2026.5.4 release and GitHub bug remediation scope; parent lineage reused under pm-rnpb."
  "2026-05-05T18:50:31.436Z",codex-release-agent,"Release prep evidence: GitHub issues #20/#21 documented, Sentry unresolved/recent issue checks were empty, private telemetry review recorded under ignored scripts/prod/telemetry/reports, compatibility-check passed for 2026.5.4 data, and node scripts/release/run-gates.mjs --telemetry-mode off --json passed all gates."
  "2026-05-05T18:52:36.635Z",codex-release-agent,"Hardened daily auto-release change detection to ignore .agents/pm-only tracker commits, so post-publish evidence/closure commits do not create a new package release by themselves. Updated release docs with npm Trusted Publishing preference and token fallback policy."
  "2026-05-05T19:00:25.963Z",codex-release-agent,"Evidence update after release-loop hardening: focused release automation regressions passed (34 tests), pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift passed, pm health --check-only passed, pm normalize --dry-run found no changes, git diff --check passed, and full node scripts/release/run-gates.mjs --telemetry-mode off --json passed with 1210 tests and 100 percent coverage."
  "2026-05-05T19:08:07.637Z",codex-release-agent,"Final pre-commit gate evidence: reran focused release automation regressions after deletion-aware tracker-only guard (34 tests passed) and reran node scripts/release/run-gates.mjs --telemetry-mode off --json. All checks passed, including 1210 tests at 100 percent coverage, secret scan, package smoke, and 2026.5.4 compatibility migration."
  "2026-05-05T19:22:09.771Z",codex-release-agent,"CI follow-up: GitHub CI run 25396714568 failed Windows Node 20 during release-automation-contract suite collection. Removed the direct .mjs helper import from the TypeScript integration test and now exercise changelog promotion through the actual script with a temp CHANGELOG file. Local Node 25 and Node 20 focused tests pass."
  "2026-05-05T19:28:28.589Z",codex-release-agent,"Post-CI-fix evidence: reran release automation contract locally under Node 25 and Node 20; reran node scripts/release/run-gates.mjs --telemetry-mode off --json and all checks passed, including 1210 tests at 100 percent coverage, secret scan, npx smoke, npm pack dry-run, compatibility migration, and Sentry threshold gate."
  "2026-05-05T19:42:42.151Z",codex-release-agent,Auto Release run 25398237876 failed before tagging because YAML parsed unquoted telemetry_mode default off as boolean false. Quoted the workflow_dispatch choice default/options and added a contract assertion so dispatch passes --telemetry-mode off as a string.
  "2026-05-05T19:52:09.967Z",codex-release-agent,"Auto-release dispatch fix evidence: workflow contract focused tests passed (38 tests) and full node scripts/release/run-gates.mjs --telemetry-mode off --json passed after quoting telemetry_mode choice values, including 1210 tests at 100 percent coverage and the 2026.5.4 compatibility gate."
  "2026-05-05T20:14:16.292Z",codex-maintainer,"Auto Release run 25399392231 failed after full gates reached the external Sentry/telemetry stage: the gate used a local sentry wrapper unavailable on GitHub runners and hid captured stderr. Hardening the release gate to use portable token/API behavior and clearer failure diagnostics before retry."
  "2026-05-05T20:23:13.078Z",codex-maintainer,"External gate hardening evidence: focused release workflow regressions passed (39 tests), unauthenticated telemetry-mode off Sentry gate returns checked=false with missing_sentry_auth_token warning, local token-backed Sentry gate reports zero fatal/error issues, and node scripts/release/run-gates.mjs --telemetry-mode off --json passed all checks with 1211 tests at 100 percent coverage."
  "2026-05-05T20:45:40.935Z",codex-maintainer,"Auto Release run 25400874495 succeeded and pushed release commit 0f04597/tag v2026.5.5, but GitHub did not start the tag-triggered Release workflow because GITHUB_TOKEN push events do not create normal workflow runs. Adding workflow_dispatch-by-tag support to Release and making Auto Release dispatch and wait for that publish workflow after a new tag is pushed."
  "2026-05-05T20:53:03.777Z",codex-maintainer,"Release dispatch automation evidence: YAML parsing passed for auto-release/release workflows, focused workflow contract tests passed (9 tests), full node scripts/release/run-gates.mjs --telemetry-mode off --json passed on version 2026.5.5 with 1211 tests at 100 percent coverage, and tracked secret scan plus diff token scan found no private token/IP leakage."
  "2026-05-05T21:01:02.871Z",codex-maintainer,"Release retry 25401715352 failed before npm publish at Sentry issue threshold: GitHub SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN is present but lacks issue-read scope and returned sentry_api_403. Adjusting release workflow so GitHub-hosted issue threshold requires SENTRY_PERSONAL_ADMIN_TOKEN, while SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN remains for release/sourcemap upload. Focused workflow contracts, YAML parse, and tracked secret scan pass."
  "2026-05-05T21:10:19.818Z",codex-maintainer,"Release retry 25402097202 successfully published npm package 2026.5.5 with provenance and passed npm/npx/bunx verification, then failed only at GitHub Release creation because workflow_dispatch runs need explicit tag_name. Updated release workflow to pass tag_name and skip duplicate npm publish when the target version already exists, making retry safe. Focused workflow contracts, YAML parse, and tracked secret scan pass."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-05T18:05:05.397Z",codex-release-agent,"External blockers from GitHub: issue #20 non-JSON frontmatter migration can brick workspaces; issue #21 git global install via npm can leave a broken symlink; latest nightly validation failed in the compatibility migration gate because npx published package execution could not find pm on PATH."
